}}The '''Witch Doctor''' is a type of [[Doctor (disambiguation)|doctor]] that can be used to cure a disease. It is most commonly used when the [[Medical Doctor]] and/or the Alternative Doctor doesn't work. If you attempt to get cured by the witch doctor, there is a chance you will be cured of your disease. Otherwise, it may kill you. If a character [[Death|dies]] from a witch doctor, it may say their "life was cut short by a witch doctor" or vaguely, "died in mysterious circumstances" but in some cases, the gravestone will say "murdered by a witch doctor", meaning it could be intentional that the witch doctor is killing. On average, the witch doctor's treatments will not cure or kill you, but could lower your [[Stats|bars]], especially your health bar. There is an [[Achievements|achievement]] you can obtain if your [[Diseases|ailment]] is cured by the witch doctor. It is believed that any disease or ailment can be cured by the witch doctor but it is rare that it will actually happen.

